### =========================
### 1) LOGIN (use existing account)
### =========================
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "sufiaanwar1975@gmail.com",
  "password": "Alvi8909!"
}

### After running:
### - Copy "accessToken" → paste above
### - Copy "refreshToken" → paste above


### =========================
### 2) GET PROFILE (should show saved info)
### =========================
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### =========================
### 3) UPDATE PROFILE (only send allowed fields)
### IMPORTANT: Do NOT send diabetes_type yet
### =========================
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alvi",
  "dob": "2001-05-10",
  "sex": "male",
  "location": "urban"
}

### After running:
### → Run GET /auth/profile again to confirm values updated.


### =========================
### 4) REFRESH TOKENS
### =========================
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### If you get new accessToken/refreshToken,
### put them in the variables at top.


### =========================
### 5) (Optional) VERIFY EMAIL
### ONLY if you have a token from backend
### =========================
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/verify-email?token=PASTE_VERIFY_TOKEN_HERE
